                   </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                   <td class="statText">
                    <pre>100</pre>
                   </td>
                  </tr>
                 </table>
                </td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                <td class="statText">
                 <pre>Returns: 0.502</pre>
                </td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                <td class="statText">
                 <table>
                  <tr>
                   <td class="statText" colspan="2">
                    In this case, we have 3 snails, and each will be carried 10.2 meters and run the remaining 0.8 meters on its own.  The total time is 0.102 + 0.4 = 0.502 hours.
                   </td>
                  </tr>
                 </table>
                </td>
               </tr>
              </table>
             </td>
